        <h2>How You Can Help</h2>
        <p>There are several ways you can contribute to recycling efforts and promote sustainability:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Reduce:</strong> Minimize waste by reducing your consumption and choosing products with minimal packaging.</li>
            <li><strong>Reuse:</strong> Reuse items whenever possible. For example, use reusable bags, bottles, and containers.</li>
            <li><strong>Recycle:</strong> Make sure to recycle correctly. Follow local recycling guidelines to ensure materials are properly sorted and clean.</li>
            <li><strong>Educate:</strong> Educate yourself and others about the importance of recycling and how to do it correctly.</li>
            <li><strong>Support Recycling Programs:</strong> Support and participate in local recycling programs and initiatives.</li>
        </ul>
